	quests: [
		{
			dependencies: ["24C3CEB85F968221"]
			description: [
				"The &lMonocrystalline Silicon Boule&r is a large crystal made of silicon which is cut up to be used as the foundation of &6integrated circuits&r. To make it, put some &8silicon dust&r in your &aEBF&r as well as some gallium arsenide."
				""
				"&4&lWARNING&r: This recipe takes &97.5&r MINUTES TO COMPLETE and uses &c&oOVER 1,000,000 EU TO COMPLETE&r! Make sure that you have a power buffer big enough or that your energy production is large enough! Alternitavely, you can make the Gas Collector to get nitrogen that you can pump in to trim the recipe time a bit. "
				"{ \"text\": \"[Gas Collector Quest]\", \"underlined\": \"true\", \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"5DFB1C69F0B8D4DB\" } }"
			]
			id: "5109EA2277F57FF7"
			subtitle: "The Monolith"
			tasks: [{
				id: "1B2993EB5F67A96B"
				item: "gtceu:silicon_boule"
				type: "item"
			}]
			x: 2.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["32B0D6DC15262F68"]
			description: [
				"To make an &bcutting saw&r powerful enough to cut silicon boules into wafers, you will need a special material for the saw. This material is &lvanadium steel&r. Vanadium steel is made in an &bMV&r mixer and smelted in an &aEBF&r. You will also need the &bMV&r electrolyzer to get chromium dust from &cruby dust&r."
				""
				"Just like the silicon boule, the recipe time can be cut by using nitrogen. To get nitrogen, you can make the"
				"{ \"text\": \"Gas Collector\", \"underlined\": \"true\", \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"5DFB1C69F0B8D4DB\" } }"
				"."
			]
			id: "719B985509257E51"
			subtitle: "Very tedious to make"
			tasks: [{
				count: 4L
				id: "77E636E284FB53F4"
				item: { Count: 4, id: "gtceu:vanadium_steel_ingot" }
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Vanadium Steel Ingot"
			x: 4.0d
			y: 1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["719B985509257E51"]
			description: ["The &ladvanced cutter&r will be a very important machine to make because it can cut &8silicon boules&r into &dwafers&r to be engraved."]
			id: "687CF89B04511124"
			subtitle: "I like yo cut G"
			tasks: [{
				id: "78DF33682385B3F4"
