		{
			dependencies: ["24C3CEB85F968221"]
			description: [
				"To progress further, you will need to upgrade some machines. Not to be faster, but to be more &opowerful&r, to unlock more &orecipes&r."
				"Right now you will need the &bMV electrolyzer&r, the &bMV mixer&r and the &bMV lathe&r."
				""
				"You will also need the &7LV sifter&r to unlock &oanother&r &bMV machine&r."
			]
