		}
		{
			dependencies: ["72BE9FE0CF888495"]
			description: ["Now that you have an &bMV emitter&r, you can make a &lLaser Engraver&r! The laser engraver can engrave your wafers to prepare them for circuit mounting and stuff. You will also need lenses, which is what the &bMV lathe&r is for."]
