		{
			dependencies: [
				"7E3663D31B94E601"
				"25AD058E02115B8A"
			]
			description: ["The last two steps of this processing line is &lILC wafers&r and &lLC chips&r. You get ILC wafers by engraving silicon wafers with an &bMV&r laser engraver, and you get LC chips by cutting your ILC wafers in an &bMV&r cutter. Now you can use the chips to make your first &6integrated circuits&r!"]
