		{
			dependencies: [
				"458499E306C79E7F"
				"3121B45962AB1250"
			]
			dependency_requirement: "one_completed"
			description: [
				"With a &6pyrolyse oven&r, you can make &8coal tar&r from coal. Then you can distill it to get &6hydrogen sulfide&r and electrolyse it to get &esulfur&r and oxygen! If you have infinite coal from excavators, you can use this processing line to get infinite &esulfur&r!"
				""
				"With a &7fluid drilling rig&r, you can distill oil into &esulfuric naphtha&r and chemically react it  with &9hydrogen&r to get &6hydrogen sulfide&r, and then electrolyse it like above."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&9Note:&r You can do any of the dependency quests to unlock this one."
			]
			icon: "gtceu:sulfur_dust"
			id: "501D1D85E81D9148"
			shape: "pentagon"
			subtitle: "It's about time!"
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "063564D4477586E0"
					item: "gtceu:lv_distillery"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "45B529CE4DF6C1C3"
					item: "gtceu:lv_electrolyzer"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "3B4219D84275FDA5"
					item: "gtceu:sulfur_dust"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "010CEB76428D87B6"
					title: "Automated"
					type: "checkmark"
				}
			]
			title: "Infinite Sulfur"
			x: 1.0d
			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1947B8EAF77F54A6"]
			description: [
				"To make polyethylene you will need to make &lethylene&r. To make ethylene, you can go the bio route or the oil route. The bio route uses wood gas from a pyrolyse oven and the oil route uses oil to turn into ethylene. Pick which one you want!"
				""
				"&9Note:&r The wood route takes less steps."
			]
			id: "30A937BEBB11984E"
			subtitle: "Chemistry Time"
			tasks: [
