			description: ["By putting ethylene in the &opolymerization chamber&r with a &5Phillips Catalyst&r &o(which you can make pretty easily in an &bMV&r&o mixer)&r you can make &lPolyethylene&r! This unlocks easier recipes for existing things and it also unlocks &6HV&r circuit components."]
