		{
			dependencies: ["32B0D6DC15262F68"]
			description: [
				"&lKanthal&r is an alloy that requires you to overclock your &aEBF&r to &6high voltage&r to smelt. Therefore, you will need 2 &bMV&r energy hatches instead of &7LV&r. You will also need very good power generation or storage, so you will need to build &bMV&r infrastructure."
				""
				"When kanthal ingots leave the &aEBF&r, you will notice that they are &every hot&r! To cool them down, you need to run them in some &9cold water&r in an &bMV&r chemical bath."
			]
